A chatbot for turntable.fm based on https://github.com/alaingilbert/Turntable-API

You need to get AUTH details to allow the bot to login. See this for how-to:
http://alaingilbert.github.com/Turntable-API/bookmarklet.html

You need to get a lastfm api key as well.

All these are defined in details.js in the same directory.

Current options are :

/song:
/song info - retreieve info about a song from lastfm
/song similar - retreive top five simialr songs from lastfm

/artist:
/artist info - retreieve info about an artist from lastfm
/artist similar - retreive top five simialr artist from lastfm